## Project Overview

- Description: Next.js/Vercel AI SDK chatbot template.
- Core Tech:
  - Next.js 15 (App Router, RSC, Server Actions)
  - Vercel AI SDK (Text, Objects, Tools)
  - shadcn/ui + Tailwind CSS
  - Drizzle ORM + Neon Postgres
  - Auth.js v5
  - Vercel Blob (Files)
- Architecture: Full-stack Next.js. Frontend (RSC/Client), Backend (API Routes/Server Actions), AI SDK integration, Postgres DB via Drizzle, Auth.js for auth, Vercel Blob for files.
